title: Episode 6: Sarah, Taylor, and Tyler (three of our PSI Talks speakers)
itunes:author: UW-Green Bay Psychology Department
itunes:summary: In this episode of 'Psychology and Stuff', Dr. Ryan Martin talks with three of the speakers for the upcoming PSI Talks (http://blog.uwgb.edu/uwgbpsych/psi-talks/).  Sarah Busko, Taylor Stelter, and Tyler Secore share why the decided to submit a talk, how they are feeling about the event, and (with no spoilers) what they plan on talking about.
